{"type":"message","id":"b6de1c22","parentId":"58b4ff05","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:42:30.409Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 11:42 EDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Check if the Mission Control data directory has any git history or backups.\n\nRun these commands:\n1. `cd /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control && git log --oneline -- data/ 2>/dev/null | head -10`\n2. `ls -la /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/`\n3. `cat /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/bills.json`\n4. `cat /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/money.json`\n5. `cat /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/habits.json`\n6. Check for any backup files: `find /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control -name \"*.bak\" -o -name \"*.backup\" -o -name \"bills*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10`\n7. Check if there's a .git directory with old data: `cd /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control && git show HEAD:data/bills.json 2>/dev/null`\n\nReport what you find. Can we recover the original data?"}],"timestamp":1774798950404}}
